                    <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Any Combat Phase</characteristic>
                    <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick an enemy unit that has no more than 1 model, that is in combat with this unit and that has charged this turn to be the target.</characteristic>
                    <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">Remove the target from the battlefield and set it up again within 1&quot; of this unit. Then, roll a D3. On a 2+, inflict an amount of mortal damage on the target equal to the roll.</characteristic>
